    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make lock blade pocket knives under 3inches legal without needing \"valid reason\"",
        "additional_details": "The majority of knife crimes are committed with kitchen knives, not pocket knives and the vast majority of people just want to be able to use a knife without worrying they will lose their fingers from the blade folding on them. Stop using law abiding knife owners as scapegoats for kitchen-knife-wielding criminals.",
        "background": "Our knife laws are extremely vague and, although it is legal to carry a lock knife if you have a \"valid reason\". People have been fined or jailed despite not causing any harm.",
